    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to summarize a news snippet about an energy transition bill and then engages in a debate regarding the socio-economic impact on coal-dependent communities. The assistant moves from a neutral summary to taking a strong, prescriptive stance in favor of the energy transition, framing the opposing view as clinging to an \"obsolete\" industry.",
